                     <interp inst="t17700425-30-off193" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing eight pair of boys leather shoes, value 26 s. and two pair of womens stuff shoes, value 2 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17700425-30-victim411" type="victimName">
                     John
